The first five thousand blind boxes are fixed as 5EOS, and then the price of the blind box will change linearly with the heat of the market. The rock bottom price is 5EOS, and every time one is sold, the price increases by 0.1EOS; if no one buys it, it lowers 0.1EOS every hour.
Tap or slice to attack, drag to move.
